<pb n="0459b" id="T21.1311.0459b" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0459b01" ed="T"/>
<milestone n="1" unit="juan"/>
<lb n="0459b02" ed="T"/><head type="no">No. 1311</head>
<lb n="0459b03" ed="T"/><juan n="001" fun="open"><mulu n="001" type="卷"/><note n="0459004" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">【原】享和二年刊長谷寺藏本</note><jhead>梵天火羅九曜</jhead></juan>
<lb n="0459b04" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0459b05" ed="T"/><div1 type="W"><p id="pT21p0459b0501"><note n="0459005" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">原本冠註曰一行禪師開元十五年入滅至咸通十五年凡百五十年是則此八十五字文後人所加</note>一行禪師修述。二十八宿在天左轉。數知
<lb n="0459b06" ed="T"/>人犯觸之位。大唐武德元年起戊寅。至咸
<lb n="0459b07" ed="T"/>通十五年甲午。都得二百五十七年矣。梵
<lb n="0459b08" ed="T"/>天火羅九曜及暗虛二星圖在此。但諸星
<lb n="0459b09" ed="T"/>都所在。看之決定。一生吉凶萬不失一神
<lb n="0459b10" ed="T"/>妙之極云云。</p></div1>
<lb n="0459b11" ed="T"/><div1 type="other"><p id="pT21p0459b1101">一羅&CB00264;蝕神星明曰。</p>
<lb n="0459b12" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0459b1201" type="dharani">唵囉戶曩阿素<note place="inline">三合</note>囉邏惹野塞麻捨&CB00418;<note n="0459006" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">野曩＝曩野&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0459006"><lem wit="【大】">野曩</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">曩野</rdg></app>
<lb n="0459b13" ed="T"/><note place="inline">名位</note>扇底伽哩莎<note n="0459007" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔婆〕－&M062403;【原】＊</note><app n="0459007"><lem wit="【大】">婆</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">&lac;</rdg></app>訶</p>
<lb n="0459b14" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0459b1401">羅&CB00264;星以錢供養口決云向丑寅供之。年一
<lb n="0459b15" ed="T"/>十十九二十八三十七四十六五十五六十四
<lb n="0459b16" ed="T"/>七十三八十二九十<note n="0459008" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">一＋（一百）&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0459008"><lem wit="【大】">一</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">一一百</rdg></app>并大凶。</p>
<lb n="0459b17" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0459b1701">
<lb n="0459b18" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0459b19" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0459b20" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0459b21" ed="T"/><note n="0459009" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">原本冠註曰龍頭各三頭都九頭本此圖一本亦在計都下</note><figure entity="FigT21045901"/></p>
<lb n="0459b22" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0459b23" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0459b24" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0459b25" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0459b26" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0459b2601">行年至此宿者凶。星隱而不見。一名羅&CB00264;。一
<lb n="0459b27" ed="T"/>名羅師。一名黃幡。一名火陽。臨人本命。憂官
<lb n="0459b28" ed="T"/>失位。重病相纏。財物破散喪服愁口舌。國王
<lb n="0459b29" ed="T"/><note n="0459010" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">原本冠註曰以神不祭蓋錯脫</note>以神不祭至此宿修福攘之。元<note n="0459011" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">神＝辰&M062485;【原】</note><sic n="0459011" resp="【原】" corr="辰">神</sic>錢畫所
<pb n="0459c" id="T21.1311.0459c" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0459c01" ed="T"/>犯神形供養大吉云云<note place="inline">人命屬大清天。此年百事如意。所求必得。行來出入皆
<lb n="0459c02" ed="T"/>大吉利</note>。</p>
<lb n="0459c03" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0459c0301">二中宮土宿星<note place="inline">王在四季</note>&CB00470;緩　真言。</p>
<lb n="0459c04" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0459c0401" type="dharani">歸命唵贊日利曳娑婆賀</p><p id="pT21p0459c0411" place="inline">又真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0459c05" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0459c0501" type="dharani">唵捨泥殺<note n="0459012" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">作＝&CB00135;&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0459012"><lem wit="【大】">作</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">&CB00135;</rdg></app><note place="inline">二合</note>羅曩乞殺<note place="inline">二合</note>怛囉<note place="inline">二合</note>跛羅
<lb n="0459c06" ed="T"/><note place="inline">二合</note>訶曩嚕<note n="0459013" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">娑＝摩婆&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0459013"><lem wit="【大】">娑</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">摩婆</rdg></app>野<note place="inline">名位</note>普瑟底<note place="inline">二合</note>迦哩娑縛<note place="inline">二
<lb n="0459c07" ed="T"/>合</note>賀</p>
<lb n="0459c08" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0459c0801"><note n="0459014" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">自又真言至賀金曜真言下出恐衍文且戍戍本作戌戌戍上字寫誤也</note>又真言。</p>
<lb n="0459c09" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0459c0901" type="dharani">唵戍戍羯囉&CB00344;馱&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>囉&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>邏&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>邏
<lb n="0459c10" ed="T"/>若<note place="inline">名位</note>室哩娑婆<note place="inline">二合</note>賀</p>
<lb n="0459c11" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0459c1101">春巽夏坤秋乾冬艮　季夏月&CB00031;子一盤祭之
<lb n="0459c12" ed="T"/>　口決云其方不定。春季向巽餘以次知之。
<lb n="0459c13" ed="T"/>年二十一二十二十九三十八四十七五十六
<lb n="0459c14" ed="T"/>六十五七十四八十三九十二并大凶。</p>
<lb n="0459c15" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0459c1501">
<lb n="0459c16" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0459c17" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0459c18" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0459c19" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0459c20" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0459c21" ed="T"/><figure entity="FigT21045902"/></p>
<lb n="0459c22" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0459c23" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0459c24" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0459c25" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0459c26" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0459c27" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0459c2701">行年至此宿者是中宮土星。其星周九十里
<lb n="0459c28" ed="T"/>屬楚國之<note n="0459015" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">分＋（野）&M062485;【原】</note><sic n="0459015" resp="【原】" corr="分野">分</sic>。其<note n="0459016" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">宿＝星&M062403;【原】＊</note><app n="0459016"><lem wit="【大】">宿</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">星</rdg></app>最凶。偏臨宮之然及<note n="0459017" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">遮＝庶&M062485;【原】</note><sic n="0459017" resp="【原】" corr="庶">遮</sic>
<lb n="0459c29" ed="T"/>人此宿貞慎疾病牢獄。君子重厄之年號曰
<pb n="0460a" id="T21.1311.0460a" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0460a01" ed="T"/>土星。不欲犯之。其形如<note n="0460001" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">波＝婆&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0460001"><lem wit="【大】">波</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">婆</rdg></app>羅門。牛冠首手
<lb n="0460a02" ed="T"/>持錫杖。與為禍國王以季<note n="0460002" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">夏＋（之）&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0460002"><lem wit="【大】">夏</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">夏之</rdg></app>月&CB00031;子一槃祭
<lb n="0460a03" ed="T"/>之。宜送本命元神錢。畫<note n="0460003" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔所犯神形〕－&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0460003"><lem wit="【大】">所犯神形</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">&lac;</rdg></app>供養。黃
<lb n="0460a04" ed="T"/>衣攘之。必消災<note n="0460004" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">增＋（長）&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0460004"><lem wit="【大】">增</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">增長</rdg></app>福壽命本命。屬赤虛天百
<lb n="0460a05" ed="T"/>事不如意。男不宜官女不宜夫。忌三月九月
<lb n="0460a06" ed="T"/>庚辛日。</p>
<lb n="0460a07" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0460a0701">三嘀北辰星<note place="inline">水星王在冬三月</note>明曰。</p>
<lb n="0460a08" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0460a0801" type="dharani">唵俱悉陀他姪佗利多崖崖紫紫&CB00135;帝莎<app source="0459007" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">婆</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">&lac;</rdg></app>
<lb n="0460a09" ed="T"/>訶</p>
<lb n="0460a10" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0460a1001">又明曰。</p>
<lb n="0460a11" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0460a1101" type="dharani">唵母馱曩乞<note n="0460005" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">殺＋（怛羅）&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0460005"><lem wit="【大】">殺</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">殺怛羅</rdg></app><note place="inline">二合</note>娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>弭曩<note place="inline">名位</note>契努<note place="inline">二
<lb n="0460a12" ed="T"/>合</note>摩莎縛<note place="inline">二合</note>賀</p>
<lb n="0460a13" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0460a1301">又心&CB00057;曰。</p>
<lb n="0460a14" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0460a1401" type="dharani">唵蘇底哩<note place="inline">二合</note>瑟吒莎<app source="0459007" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">婆</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">&lac;</rdg></app>訶</p>
<lb n="0460a15" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0460a1501">以中夏之月用油祭向北方供之年三十二二
<lb n="0460a16" ed="T"/>十一三十三十九四十八五十七六十六七十
<lb n="0460a17" ed="T"/>五八十四九十三少<note n="0460006" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">吉＝凶&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0460006"><lem wit="【大】">吉</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">凶</rdg></app>。</p>
<lb n="0460a18" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0460a1801">
<lb n="0460a19" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0460a20" ed="T"/><figure entity="FigT21046001"/></p>
<lb n="0460a21" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0460a22" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0460a23" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0460a2301">行年至此<app source="0459016" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">宿</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">星</rdg></app>名北辰。一名毚星一名滴星。周
<lb n="0460a24" ed="T"/>迴一百里屬燕趙之分野。若臨人本命。主陰
<lb n="0460a25" ed="T"/>愁口舌盜賊牽喚。其神狀婦人。頭首戴猿冠
<lb n="0460a26" ed="T"/>手持紙筆。國王以仲夏之月用油祭。宜醮北
<lb n="0460a27" ed="T"/>斗穰之。數此十二宮。從生月下一宿為一日。
<lb n="0460a28" ed="T"/>左數至生日止即知也云云。已行無<note place="inline">異本</note>人命
<lb n="0460a29" ed="T"/>屬遊咸天百事不成。男不宜官女不宜夫。忌
<pb n="0460b" id="T21.1311.0460b" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0460b01" ed="T"/>四月丙戌日。</p>
<lb n="0460b02" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0460b0201">四西方大白星<note place="inline">金星<note n="0460007" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">金＋（土）&M062403;【原】，（火）&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0460007"><lem wit="【大】">金</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">金土</rdg><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">金火</rdg></app>神也王在秋三月</note>明曰。</p>
<lb n="0460b03" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0460b0301" type="dharani">歸命唵吠尾<note n="0460008" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">毘＝野&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0460008"><lem wit="【大】">毘</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">野</rdg></app>娑婆訶</p>
<lb n="0460b04" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0460b0401">又真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0460b05" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0460b0501" type="dharani">唵戍<note place="inline">上</note>羯囉&CB00344;馱&CB00085;<note n="0460009" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔馱&CB00085;〕－&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0460009"><lem wit="【大】">馱&CB00085;</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">&lac;</rdg></app><note place="inline">二合</note><note n="0460010" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（羅&CB00085;二合）＋邏&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0460010"><lem wit="【大】">邏</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">羅&CB00085;二合邏</rdg></app><note n="0460011" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">若＋（野）&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0460011"><lem wit="【大】">若</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">若野</rdg></app><note place="inline">名位</note>室
<lb n="0460b06" ed="T"/><note n="0460012" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">哩＋（迦里）&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0460012"><lem wit="【大】">哩</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">哩迦里</rdg></app>娑婆訶</p>
<lb n="0460b07" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0460b0701">常以仲<note n="0460013" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">秋＝夏&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0460013"><lem wit="【大】">秋</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">夏</rdg></app>之月用生錢祭之向。西方供之年
<lb n="0460b08" ed="T"/>四十三二十二三十一四十四十九五十八六
<lb n="0460b09" ed="T"/>十七七十六八十五九十四少凶。</p>
<lb n="0460b10" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0460b1001">
<lb n="0460b11" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0460b12" ed="T"/><figure entity="FigT21046002"/></p>
<lb n="0460b13" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0460b14" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0460b15" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0460b16" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0460b1601">行年至那<note n="0460014" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">頡＋（者）&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0460014"><lem wit="【大】">頡</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">頡者</rdg></app>■。<note n="0460015" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔是〕－&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0460015"><lem wit="【大】">是</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">&lac;</rdg></app>太白星西方金精<note n="0460016" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔也〕－&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0460016"><lem wit="【大】">也</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">&lac;</rdg></app>。其
<lb n="0460b17" ed="T"/>星一名大白。一名長庚。一名那頡。其星周迴
<lb n="0460b18" ed="T"/>一百里屬秦國之分野。若臨人<note n="0460017" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔年〕－&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0460017"><lem wit="【大】">年</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">&lac;</rdg></app>本命。<note n="0460018" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">至＝主&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0460018"><lem wit="【大】">至</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">主</rdg></app>
<lb n="0460b19" ed="T"/>有哭泣刀兵。形如女人。頭戴<note n="0460019" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">首＝酉&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0460019"><lem wit="【大】">首</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">酉</rdg></app>冠。白練衣
<lb n="0460b20" ed="T"/>彈絃。與人為患。國王常以仲秋之月用生錢
<lb n="0460b21" ed="T"/>祭之。行年至此星。宜著白衣醮謝本命元神
<lb n="0460b22" ed="T"/>作福田。大吉也。人命屬飛<note n="0460020" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">揰＝拄&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0460020"><lem wit="【大】">揰</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">拄</rdg></app>天百事皆吉
<lb n="0460b23" ed="T"/><note n="0460021" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔憂〕－&M062485;【原】</note><sic n="0460021" resp="【原】" corr="＆lac；">憂</sic>解患。男財宜官婦子相係。治生萬倍。</p>
<lb n="0460b24" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0460b2401">五大陽<note n="0460022" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">密＝蜜&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0460022"><lem wit="【大】">密</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">蜜</rdg></app>日<note n="0460023" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">星＝曰&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0460023"><lem wit="【大】">星</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">曰</rdg></app>真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0460b25" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0460b2501" type="dharani">曩謨羅怛曩<note place="inline">二合</note>怛羅夜<note place="inline">引</note>野曩莫素哩野薩
<lb n="0460b26" ed="T"/>縛曩乞<note n="0460024" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">羅＝灑&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0460024"><lem wit="【大】">羅</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">灑</rdg></app><note place="inline">二合</note>怛囉<note place="inline">二合</note>羅惹野唵阿謨伽<note n="0460025" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">寫＋（野）&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0460025"><lem wit="【大】">寫</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">寫野</rdg></app>
<lb n="0460b27" ed="T"/><note place="inline">名位</note>設底<note place="inline">去</note>莎<app source="0459007" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">婆</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">&lac;</rdg></app>訶</p>
<lb n="0460b28" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0460b2801">以冬至之日用眾寶祭之。向卯辰供之年五
<lb n="0460b29" ed="T"/>十四二十三三十二四十一五十五十九六十
<pb n="0460c" id="T21.1311.0460c" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0460c01" ed="T"/>八七十七八十六九十五大吉。</p>
<lb n="0460c02" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0460c0201">行年至此宿者。主大陽屬日。其星周迴一千
<lb n="0460c03" ed="T"/>五百里。一日一周天。若臨人本命。加官進祿
<lb n="0460c04" ed="T"/>有喜事。<note n="0460026" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">常＝當&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0460026"><lem wit="【大】">常</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">當</rdg></app>得貴人接引。所作通達。國王以
<lb n="0460c05" ed="T"/>冬至之日用眾寶祭之大吉矣　此星真言不
<lb n="0460c06" ed="T"/>可思議。若<note n="0460027" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">至＝志&M062403;【原】＊</note><app n="0460027"><lem wit="【大】">至</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">志</rdg></app>心帶佩并供養一年。非橫不死
<lb n="0460c07" ed="T"/>云云。人命屬通<note n="0460028" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">光＋（天）&M062485;【原】</note><sic n="0460028" resp="【原】" corr="光天">光</sic>■百事如意。天神相保終
<lb n="0460c08" ed="T"/>無實難。所向開通福祿自至。</p>
<lb n="0460c09" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0460c0901">
<lb n="0460c10" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0460c11" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0460c12" ed="T"/><note n="0460029" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">原本冠註曰此圖一本在莫曰大陰下</note><figure entity="FigT21046003"/></p>
<lb n="0460c13" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0460c14" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0460c15" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0460c16" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0460c17" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0460c1701">六南方火熒惑星<note place="inline">火王在夏三月</note>火星真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0460c18" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0460c1801" type="dharani">歸命唵摩<note n="0460030" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔訶〕－&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0460030"><lem wit="【大】">訶</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">&lac;</rdg></app>利多莎<app source="0459007" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">婆</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">&lac;</rdg></app>訶</p>
<lb n="0460c19" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0460c1901">又真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0460c20" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0460c2001" type="dharani">唵阿&CB00344;羅迦嚕儗野<note place="inline">名位</note>娑婆<note place="inline">二合</note>賀</p>
<lb n="0460c21" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0460c2101">以仲夏之月火祭之。向南方供之。年六十五
<lb n="0460c22" ed="T"/>二十四三十三四十二五十一六十六十九七
<lb n="0460c23" ed="T"/>十八八十七九十六並是凶年也。</p>
<lb n="0460c24" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0460c2401">行年至此星。一名南方熒惑星。一名<note n="0460031" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">四利＝罰星&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0460031"><lem wit="【大】">四利</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">罰星</rdg></app>
<lb n="0460c25" ed="T"/>星。一名<note n="0460032" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">虛＝雲&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0460032"><lem wit="【大】">虛</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">雲</rdg></app>漢。其星周迴七十里。屬魏國之
<lb n="0460c26" ed="T"/>分。若臨人命。必生口舌。疾病相纏。神形如外
<lb n="0460c27" ed="T"/>道。首戴驢冠。四手兵器刀刃。國王以仲夏之
<lb n="0460c28" ed="T"/>月。用火祭之。行年至此者。君子<note n="0460033" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">臨＝修&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0460033"><lem wit="【大】">臨</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">修</rdg></app>福。職事
<lb n="0460c29" ed="T"/>進益。小人臨<note n="0460034" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">福＝禍&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0460034"><lem wit="【大】">福</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">禍</rdg></app>。災害不生。敬之即無殃咎。
<pb n="0461a" id="T21.1311.0461a" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0461a01" ed="T"/>人命屬雲霄。天神相保。不敢&CB00617;禍。錢財滿盈。
<lb n="0461a02" ed="T"/>福祿廣至。雖有少憂。自解無苦。</p>
<lb n="0461a03" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0461a0301">
<lb n="0461a04" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0461a05" ed="T"/><figure entity="FigT21046101"/></p>
<lb n="0461a06" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0461a07" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0461a08" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0461a0801">七計都蝕神星明曰。</p>
<lb n="0461a09" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0461a0901" type="dharani">唵縛日羅<note place="inline">二合</note>計都曩<note place="inline">引</note>曩乞殺<note place="inline">二合</note>怛羅<note place="inline">二合</note>
<lb n="0461a10" ed="T"/>邏惹野<note place="inline">名位</note><note n="0461001" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">吽＋（娑婆賀）&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0461001"><lem wit="【大】">吽</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">吽娑婆賀</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0461a11" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0461a1101">畫此形深室供養禳之。迴禍為福。向未申供
<lb n="0461a12" ed="T"/>之。羅&CB00264;帶<note n="0461002" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">珠＝二&CB14648;&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0461002"><lem wit="【大】">珠</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">二&CB14648;</rdg></app>寶。並日月計都著錦繡衣。年
<lb n="0461a13" ed="T"/>七十六二十五三十四四十三五十二六十
<lb n="0461a14" ed="T"/><note n="0461003" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">一＋（七十）&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0461003"><lem wit="【大】">一</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">一七十</rdg></app>七十九八十八九十七並凶也。</p>
<lb n="0461a15" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0461a1501">行年至此計都亦是隱星。一名豹<note n="0461004" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">尾＋（一名蝕神尾）&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0461004"><lem wit="【大】">尾</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">尾一名蝕神尾</rdg></app>。一名大
<lb n="0461a16" ed="T"/>隱。首隱不見。不見<note n="0461005" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔而〕－&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0461005"><lem wit="【大】">而</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">&lac;</rdg></app>行無定形。若臨人名。
<lb n="0461a17" ed="T"/><note n="0461006" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">官＋（室）&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0461006"><lem wit="【大】">官</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">官室</rdg></app>最多逼塞。求官不遂。務被遷移。官符相
<lb n="0461a18" ed="T"/>纏。多憂疾病。此星凶。國王不<note n="0461007" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">原本冠註曰祭下蓋有脫文</note>祭。</p>
<lb n="0461a19" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0461a1901">
<lb n="0461a20" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0461a21" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0461a22" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0461a23" ed="T"/><note n="0461008" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">原本冠註曰龍頭各一頭都三頭本此圖一本亦在羅&CB00264;下</note><figure entity="FigT21046102"/></p>
<lb n="0461a24" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0461a25" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0461a26" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0461a27" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0461a28" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0461a2801">行年至此須送五道司命。畫此神形。深室供
<lb n="0461a29" ed="T"/>養禳之。迴禍作福。人命屬溫獨天。所向不如
<pb n="0461b" id="T21.1311.0461b" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0461b01" ed="T"/>意。行■無利。夫婦哭泣。或夫流淚。忌五月六
<lb n="0461b02" ed="T"/>月甲乙日。</p>
<lb n="0461b03" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0461b0301">八<note n="0461009" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">暮＝莫日&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0461009"><lem wit="【大】">暮</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">莫日</rdg></app>大陰<note place="inline">月天</note>明曰。</p>
<lb n="0461b04" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0461b0401" type="dharani">唵戰<note place="inline">上</note>怛羅<note place="inline">二合</note>曩乞灑<note place="inline">二合引</note>怛羅<note place="inline">二合</note>邏惹野<note place="inline">名
<lb n="0461b05" ed="T"/>位</note><note n="0461010" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（唵阿謨伽寫）＋設&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0461010"><lem wit="【大】">設</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">唵阿謨伽寫設</rdg></app>底娑婆賀</p>
<lb n="0461b06" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0461b0601">常以夏至之日。眾寶玉及水祭之向申酉供
<lb n="0461b07" ed="T"/>之。年八十七二十六三十五四十四五十三
<lb n="0461b08" ed="T"/>六十二七十一八十八十九九十八。</p>
<lb n="0461b09" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0461b0901">
<lb n="0461b10" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0461b11" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0461b12" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0461b13" ed="T"/><note n="0461011" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">原本冠註曰此圖一本在蜜日大陽下</note><figure entity="FigT21046103"/></p>
<lb n="0461b14" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0461b15" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0461b16" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0461b17" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0461b18" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0461b1801">行年至此宿位者。是<note n="0461012" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">太＝大&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0461012"><lem wit="【大】">太</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">大</rdg></app>陰。也屬月。其月周
<lb n="0461b19" ed="T"/>迴一千五百里。一日周迴天下。若臨人本命
<lb n="0461b20" ed="T"/>大吉。加官進祿所作通達。得貴人接引。長有
<lb n="0461b21" ed="T"/>喜慶之事。國王以夏至之日。用眾珍玉及水
<lb n="0461b22" ed="T"/>祭之。行年至此<note n="0461013" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">方＝萬&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0461013"><lem wit="【大】">方</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">萬</rdg></app>。事通和求官得遂所作大
<lb n="0461b23" ed="T"/>吉。人命屬微<note n="0461014" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">供＝借&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0461014"><lem wit="【大】">供</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">借</rdg></app>天千百事皆凶。遭病恐死田
<lb n="0461b24" ed="T"/>蠶不收憂縣官事。忌正月九月丙丁日。</p>
<lb n="0461b25" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0461b2501">九東方歲星<note place="inline">王在春三月</note>木星明曰。</p>
<lb n="0461b26" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0461b2601" type="dharani">曩謨三曼多沒馱喃唵印那羅野娑婆訶</p><p id="pT21p0461b2617" place="inline">又
<lb n="0461b27" ed="T"/>真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0461b28" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0461b2801" type="dharani">唵婆羅<note place="inline">二合</note>訶薩&CB00425;<note place="inline">二合</note>底曩摩<note n="0461015" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔地〕－&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0461015"><lem wit="【大】">地</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">&lac;</rdg></app>比跢縛曩
<lb n="0461b29" ed="T"/><note place="inline">二合</note>野<note place="inline">名位</note>摩&CB00256;縛<note n="0461016" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（羅）＋&CB00501;&M062403;【原】</note><note n="0461016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（羅）＋<app><lem resp="CBETA.Maha">馱</lem><rdg wit="【大】">&CB00501;</rdg></app>&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0461016"><lem wit="【大】">馱</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">羅馱</rdg></app><note place="inline">二合</note>寧婆縛<note place="inline">二合</note>賀<note place="inline">引</note></p>
<pb n="0461c" id="T21.1311.0461c" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0461c01" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0461c0101">常以仲春月用眾寶祭之。向東供之。年九十
<lb n="0461c02" ed="T"/>八二十七三十六四十五五十四六十三七十
<lb n="0461c03" ed="T"/>二八十一九十九十九並是大吉。</p>
<lb n="0461c04" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0461c0401">行年至嗢沒斯者是歲星。東方木精。<note n="0461017" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔一〕－&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0461017"><lem wit="【大】">一</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">&lac;</rdg></app>名攝
<lb n="0461c05" ed="T"/>提。其星周迴一百里屬魯衛之分。臨人本命。
<lb n="0461c06" ed="T"/>加官進祿。萬事吉祥。其神形如卿相。著青衣。
<lb n="0461c07" ed="T"/>戴亥冠。手執華<note n="0461018" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB00031;＝葉&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0461018"><lem wit="【大】">&CB00031;</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">葉</rdg></app>。國王常以仲春月。用眾
<lb n="0461c08" ed="T"/>寶祭之。</p>
<lb n="0461c09" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0461c0901">
<lb n="0461c10" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0461c11" ed="T"/><note n="0461019" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">原本冠註曰此圖一本大異</note><figure entity="FigT21046104"/></p>
<lb n="0461c12" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0461c13" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0461c14" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0461c1401">行年至此宿宜與貴人交通婚姻和合。此<note n="0461020" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">年＋（進口）&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0461020"><lem wit="【大】">年</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">年進口</rdg></app>
<lb n="0461c15" ed="T"/>■■大吉之<note n="0461021" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">事＝年&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0461021"><lem wit="【大】">事</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">年</rdg></app>也。人命屬高倉天萬事皆諧。
<lb n="0461c16" ed="T"/>所向如意往來有利。居為平安子孫熾昌。</p>
<lb n="0461c17" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0461c1701"><note n="0461022" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">原本冠註曰已以異本無之蓋是後人雜記</note>北斗七星明曰。</p>
<lb n="0461c18" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0461c1801" type="dharani">曩莫三曼多那羅那羅破左邏吽</p>
<lb n="0461c19" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0461c1901">九執明曰。</p>
<lb n="0461c20" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0461c2001" type="dharani">歸命唵&CB00617;羅<note place="inline">二</note>醯涅&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>哩也<note place="inline">二合</note>&CB00425;囉&CB00425;多
<lb n="0461c21" ed="T"/><note place="inline">二合</note>&CB04057;底囉摩野<note place="inline">三</note>娑婆<note place="inline">二合</note>賀</p>
<lb n="0461c22" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0461c2201">蝕神頭從正月至年終常<note n="0461023" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">居＋（此）&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0461023"><lem wit="【大】">居</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">居此</rdg></app>二宿<figure entity="FigT21046105"/><figure entity="FigT21046106"/>
<lb n="0461c23" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0461c24" ed="T"/><figure entity="FigT21046107"/><figure entity="FigT21046108"/><figure entity="FigT21046109"/>翼宿<figure entity="FigT21046110"/><note n="0461024" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">原本冠註曰張一本作方弓片字歟</note>張
<lb n="0461c25" ed="T"/>宿<note place="inline">羅</note><figure entity="FigT21046111"/><note n="0461025" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">尾＝扈&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0461025"><lem wit="【大】">尾</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">扈</rdg></app>宿<figure entity="FigT21046112"/>
<lb n="0461c26" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0461c27" ed="T"/>低宿<note place="inline">計</note>蝕神尾從正月至年終<note n="0461026" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">帶＝常&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0461026"><lem wit="【大】">帶</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">常</rdg></app>居此二宿
<lb n="0461c28" ed="T"/><note place="inline">以上無異本</note>按聿斯經云。凡人只知有七曜<note n="0461027" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">原本冠註曰不下脫知字次晴字誤也</note>不晴虛
<lb n="0461c29" ed="T"/>星號曰羅&CB00264;計都。此星在<note n="0461028" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">隱位＝位隱&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0461028"><lem wit="【大】">隱位</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">位隱</rdg></app>而不見。逢日
<pb n="0462a" id="T21.1311.0462a" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0462a01" ed="T"/>月即蝕。號曰蝕神。計都者蝕神之尾也。<note n="0462001" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">號＋（曰）&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0462001"><lem wit="【大】">號</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">號曰</rdg></app>
<lb n="0462a02" ed="T"/>豹尾。若行年到此宿。切須畫所犯神形。深室
<lb n="0462a03" ed="T"/>供養燒錢攘之。即災害不生。若遇惡星須攘
<lb n="0462a04" ed="T"/>之。諸不逆其所犯。即變凶成吉。<note n="0462002" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（若）＋不&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0462002"><lem wit="【大】">不</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">若不</rdg></app>信即變
<lb n="0462a05" ed="T"/>吉成凶。遇吉星喜慶重重福德自<note n="0462003" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">在＝至&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0462003"><lem wit="【大】">在</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">至</rdg></app>。遇惡星
<lb n="0462a06" ed="T"/>災害競生。王侯犯之即謫官降職。但以亥時
<lb n="0462a07" ed="T"/>面向北斗。<app source="0460027" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">至</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">志</rdg></app>心祭<note n="0462004" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔拜〕－&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0462004"><lem wit="【大】">拜</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">&lac;</rdg></app>本命星。切不得向北
<lb n="0462a08" ed="T"/>小便折人壽命。宜<note n="0462005" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔思〕－&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0462005"><lem wit="【大】">思</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">&lac;</rdg></app>真念<note n="0462006" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">善＋（根）&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0462006"><lem wit="【大】">善</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">善根</rdg></app>獲福宜財。若
<lb n="0462a09" ed="T"/>不<note n="0462007" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔穰〕－&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0462007"><lem wit="【大】">穰</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">&lac;</rdg></app>之災害競起。</p></div1>
<lb n="0462a10" ed="T"/><div1 type="other"><mulu level="1" n="2" label="葛仙公禮北斗法" type="其他"/><head>葛仙公禮北斗法</head>
<lb n="0462a11" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0462a1101">鎮上玄<note n="0462008" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">九＝元&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0462008"><lem wit="【大】">九</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">元</rdg></app><note n="0462009" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔北〕－&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0462009"><lem wit="【大】">北</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">&lac;</rdg></app>極北斗。從王侯及於士庶。盡
<lb n="0462a12" ed="T"/>皆屬北斗七星。常須敬重。<note n="0462010" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">當＝常&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0462010"><lem wit="【大】">當</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">常</rdg></app>不逢橫禍凶惡
<lb n="0462a13" ed="T"/>之事。遍救世人之<note n="0462011" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">襄＝衰&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0462011"><lem wit="【大】">襄</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">衰</rdg></app>厄。得延年益算無諸災
<lb n="0462a14" ed="T"/>難。并本命元神<app source="0460027" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">至</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">志</rdg></app>心供養。皆得<note n="0462012" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB05270;＝稱&M062403;【原】</note><note n="0462012" resp="CBETA" type="mod"><app><lem resp="CBETA.Maha">&CB04210;</lem><rdg wit="【大】">&CB05270;</rdg></app>＝稱&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0462012"><lem wit="【大】">&CB04210;</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">稱</rdg></app>遂人之
<lb n="0462a15" ed="T"/>命祿。災害殃咎迷<note n="0462013" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">塞＋（騫）&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0462013"><lem wit="【大】">塞</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">塞騫</rdg></app><note n="0462014" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB00612;＝稱&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0462014"><lem wit="【大】">&CB00612;</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">稱</rdg></app>。皆由不敬星像。不
<lb n="0462a16" ed="T"/>知有犯星辰。黯黯而行災難自然來至。攘之
<lb n="0462a17" ed="T"/>即大吉也。祭本命元神日。一年有六日。但至
<lb n="0462a18" ed="T"/>心本命日。用好紙剪隨年錢。用茶&CB00031;三疊淨
<lb n="0462a19" ed="T"/>床一鋪。焚香虔心面視北斗。再拜啟告曰。隔
<lb n="0462a20" ed="T"/>居少人好道求<note n="0462015" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">靈＝虛&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0462015"><lem wit="【大】">靈</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">虛</rdg></app>常見尊儀。本命日謹<note n="0462016" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">奉＋（上）&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0462016"><lem wit="【大】">奉</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">奉上</rdg></app>
<lb n="0462a21" ed="T"/>銀錢仙&CB00031;。供養於北斗辰<note n="0462017" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔星〕－&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0462017"><lem wit="【大】">星</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">&lac;</rdg></app>并本命神<note n="0462018" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">形＝願&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0462018"><lem wit="【大】">形</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">願</rdg></app>。
<lb n="0462a22" ed="T"/><note n="0462019" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">將＝得&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0462019"><lem wit="【大】">將</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">得</rdg></app>長<note n="0462020" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔是〕－&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0462020"><lem wit="【大】">是</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">&lac;</rdg></app>生益壽無諸橫禍。神魂為安。元神
<lb n="0462a23" ed="T"/>自在。<note n="0462021" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">襄年凡＝衰年厄月&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0462021"><lem wit="【大】">襄年凡</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">衰年厄月</rdg></app>■驅向遠方。再拜燒錢合掌供
<lb n="0462a24" ed="T"/>養。</p>
<lb n="0462a25" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0462a2501">　　┌○破軍星持大<note n="0462022" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">置＝京&M062485;【原】</note><sic n="0462022" resp="【原】" corr="京">置</sic><note place="inline">午生人</note></p>
<lb n="0462a26" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0462a2601">○─○武曲星賓大東<note place="inline">巳未生人屬云云</note></p>
<lb n="0462a27" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0462a2701">　　└○廉貞星不灌子<note place="inline">辰申生人</note></p>
<lb n="0462a28" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0462a2801">　　　└○文曲星微慧子<note place="inline">卯酉生人</note></p>
<lb n="0462a29" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0462a2901">　　　　├○祿存星祿會<note place="inline">寅戌生人</note></p>
<pb n="0462b" id="T21.1311.0462b" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0462b01" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0462b0101">　　┌─┴○巨門星貞文子<note place="inline">亥丑生人</note></p>
<lb n="0462b02" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0462b0201">　　○貪狼星司希子<note place="inline">子生人</note></p>
<lb n="0462b03" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0462b0301">凡祿命書云云。</p>
<lb n="0462b04" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0462b0401">屬破軍星人。日食一升餘命八十歲　男女
<lb n="0462b05" ed="T"/>午年字大京子。</p>
<lb n="0462b06" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0462b0601">屬武曲星人。日食一石餘命八十五歲　巳
<lb n="0462b07" ed="T"/>未年男女字大東子。</p>
<lb n="0462b08" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0462b0801">屬廉貞星人。日食一升餘命八十歲　辰申
<lb n="0462b09" ed="T"/>年男女字<note n="0462023" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">術＝衛&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0462023"><lem wit="【大】">術</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">衛</rdg></app>不&CB00444;子。</p>
<lb n="0462b10" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0462b1001">屬文曲星人。日食四升餘命九十歲　卯酉
<lb n="0462b11" ed="T"/>年男女字微慧字。</p>
<lb n="0462b12" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0462b1201">屬祿存星人。日食五升餘命八十歲　寅戌
<lb n="0462b13" ed="T"/>年男女字祿存會子。</p>
<lb n="0462b14" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0462b1401">屬巨門星人。日食八升餘命八十歲　丑亥
<lb n="0462b15" ed="T"/>年男女字貞文子。</p>
<lb n="0462b16" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0462b1601">屬貪狼星人。日食二升餘命六十五歲　子
<lb n="0462b17" ed="T"/>年男女字司希神子。</p>
<lb n="0462b18" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0462b1801">一切如來說破一切宿曜障吉祥真言</p>
<lb n="0462b19" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0462b1901" type="dharani">唵薩縛諾<note n="0462024" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">剎＝利&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0462024"><lem wit="【大】">剎</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">利</rdg></app>怛羅<note place="inline">二合</note>三磨曳室哩曳扇底迦
<lb n="0462b20" ed="T"/>俱嚕娑婆<note place="inline">二合</note>賀</p>
<lb n="0462b21" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0462b2101">男忌天羅女忌地網欲知衰禍但在行年所犯
<lb n="0462b22" ed="T"/>無不知也　夫人行年吉少凶多乍可知而迴
<lb n="0462b23" ed="T"/>避不可坐<note n="0462025" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">受＝禱&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0462025"><lem wit="【大】">受</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">禱</rdg></app>其災<note n="0462026" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">云＋（也）&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0462026"><lem wit="【大】">云</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">云也</rdg></app>若莫<note n="0462027" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">日＋（滅）&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0462027"><lem wit="【大】">日</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">日滅</rdg></app>　■■。</p></div1>
<lb n="0462b24" ed="T"/><div1 type="other"><mulu level="1" n="3" label="梵天火羅圖" type="其他"/><head>梵天火羅圖一帖</head>
<lb n="0462b25" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0462b2501">敬白大梵天王帝釋天王。閻羅天子五道大
<lb n="0462b26" ed="T"/>神。太山府君司命司祿。十二宮神七曜九執。
<lb n="0462b27" ed="T"/>二十八宿藥叉藥叉女。毘舍遮毘舍支步多
<lb n="0462b28" ed="T"/>那天等。殊別當所鎮守護法善神。若家內守
<lb n="0462b29" ed="T"/>宅諸大小神等。并三千大千世界不可說不
<pb n="0462c" id="T21.1311.0462c" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0462c01" ed="T"/>可說微塵剎土六道四生類。某甲願今月吉
<lb n="0462c02" ed="T"/>日良時。設神供無遮供具。其大志者可知心
<lb n="0462c03" ed="T"/>云云。</p>
<lb n="0462c04" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0462c0401">次勸請　向東方合掌　已上畢。</p>
<lb n="0462c05" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0462c0501">　<note place="inline">已下表紙袖書也今此記之</note>。</p>
<lb n="0462c06" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0462c0601">　一<note place="inline">羅&CB00264;大惡</note>二<note place="inline">土少惡</note>三<note place="inline">水中吉</note>四<note place="inline">金<note n="0462028" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">中＝大&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0462028"><lem wit="【大】">中</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">大</rdg></app>吉</note>五<note place="inline">日大吉</note>六<note place="inline">火少惡</note>七
<lb n="0462c07" ed="T"/><note place="inline">計大<note n="0462029" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">吉＝惡&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0462029"><lem wit="【大】">吉</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">惡</rdg></app></note>八<note place="inline">月中吉</note>九<note place="inline">木大吉</note>。</p>
<lb n="0462c08" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0462c0801">名一切少天&CB00057;法<note place="inline">以右手中指直。餘指作拳。左手亦然。二手合腕去心胸八寸。右手中
<lb n="0462c09" ed="T"/>指少屈。坤左中&CB04160;節來去。動令忿</note>。</p>
<lb n="0462c10" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0462c1001">諸天通用&CB00057;</p>
<lb n="0462c11" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0462c1101" type="dharani">　唵路<note n="0462030" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">迦＋（路迦）&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0462030"><lem wit="【大】">迦</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">迦路迦</rdg></app>　迦路野<note n="0462031" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">曳＋（迦路野曳）&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0462031"><lem wit="【大】">曳</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">曳迦路野曳</rdg></app>　娑婆賀</p></div1>
<lb n="0462c12" ed="T"/><div1 type="W"><p id="pT21p0462c1201">文治五年八月書寫。以四本挍之。玄證正
<lb n="0462c13" ed="T"/>德三<note n="0462032" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（癸）＋已&M062403;【原】</note><note n="0462032" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（癸）＋<app><lem resp="CBETA.Maha">巳</lem><rdg wit="【大】">已</rdg></app>&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0462032"><lem wit="【大】">巳</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">癸巳</rdg></app>年。以&CB01267;尾本寫之。慧旭寬延四年
<lb n="0462c14" ed="T"/>書之<note n="0462033" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（權僧正）＋宥&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0462033"><lem wit="【大】">宥</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">權僧正宥</rdg></app>證　明和四<note n="0462034" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（丁）＋亥&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0462034"><lem wit="【大】">亥</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">丁亥</rdg></app>年以御室真乘院
<lb n="0462c15" ed="T"/>法務前大僧正宥證大和尚本寫挍。智積
<lb n="0462c16" ed="T"/>院動潮　寬政五丑年以右本書之。洛北
<lb n="0462c17" ed="T"/>福勝密寺秀陽享和二壬戌冬以件本挍正
<lb n="0462c18" ed="T"/>上木行於普天。</p>
<lb n="0462c19" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0462c1901">　和州豐山長谷寺歡喜院沙門快道記</p>
<lb n="0462c20" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0462c2001">以傳領之本對挍加筆畢　　慈順</p>
<lb n="0462c21" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0462c2101">文政三歲次庚辰季秋朔日以秀陽闍梨去
<lb n="0462c22" ed="T"/>享和三年住豐山之日令密榮傳寫之本於
<lb n="0462c23" ed="T"/>東武湯島根生役寮自手寫挍之了</p>
